name: Aberdeen PHP
body:
### Aberdeen's Regular PHP User Group!

## When?
The first wednesday of the month (next meetup is 6th of May), starting 6:30 for 7

## Where?
Fifth Ring conference room
<iframe src="https://mapsengine.google.com/map/u/0/embed?mid=zavZj8x3a3lU.k2DYlbQ1KAc4" width="640" height="480"></iframe>

## What?
Monthly meetup where we will talk about all things web, with a bit of a bias for PHP.

## Who?
Anyone's welcome to come along, we hang out on Slack so if you want to join the chat ping us a message on twitter @AberdeenPHP or contact me directly danny@iamdannywilson.com / @iamdannywilson on twitter
